This is my heater.

24:11.369 --> 24:14.664
- I dare you to hit it.
- You'll be sorry.

24:14.748 --> 24:17.334
- Give that boy a bigger bat.
- You want the heater,
I'll give it to you.

24:17.417 --> 24:19.961
Give him a basketball.
Maybe then he'll hit it.

24:24.966 --> 24:27.135
Oh, man!

24:27.218 --> 24:30.388
Yeah!
That's how you do it.

24:32.515 --> 24:35.018
