24:37.395 --> 24:40.231
Hit me with the heater.

24:40.315 --> 24:42.484
Stupid idiot!

24:42.567 --> 24:45.695
Low and outside.
Just like I like it.

24:56.748 --> 24:58.667
I'm gonna hit you!

24:58.750 --> 25:03.838
Wait a sec. I'll get it.
- 1932 called shot
World Series by The Babe.

25:03.922 --> 25:06.591
Called shot by the Babe.

25:06.716 --> 25:08.885
No!

25:08.969 --> 25:12.597
No!

25:18.061 --> 25:21.690
- Smalls, come back!
- Hey guys, I'll get it!

25:21.773 --> 25:24.150
- Smalls!
- Smalls!

25:24.275 --> 25:27.278
- What are you doing?
- Smalls, wait!

25:27.404 --> 25:30.073
- Guys, what are you--
- Smalls!

25:30.156 --> 25:32.701
Get off!
Guys, I gotta get the ball!

25:32.784 --> 25:36.871
- No, wait!
- Get off of me! Now!

25:36.955 --> 25:38.873
- You're gonna get yourself killed!
- Killed, man, jeez!

25:38.957 --> 25:40.875
Stop!

25:42.961 --> 25:45.046
Holy crap,
you could've been killed.

25:45.130 --> 25:47.299
Yeah, yeah, truly.
What are you doing?

25:47.424 --> 25:50.260
You guys were leaving,
so I just thought I'd hop the fence--

25:50.343 --> 25:53.930
- If you were thinking, you
wouldn't have thought that.
- You can't go back there.

25:54.014 --> 25:56.391
- Then how do we get the ball back?
- We don't.

25:56.474 --> 25:58.393
- We don't.
- It's history.

25:58.476 --> 26:02.063
- It's history. Kiss it--
- Kiss it good-bye. Shut up, Tommy.

26:02.147 --> 26:04.649
It's gone, man. Gone.

26:04.774 --> 26:08.236
Game's over, man.
We'll just get another ball tomorrow.

26:08.320 --> 26:10.822
- Yeah.
- We'll never see it again.

26:10.947 --> 26:13.616
Why not?

26:17.037 --> 26:18.955
The Beast.

26:19.039 --> 26:21.082
What is that?

26:26.296 --> 26:28.173
Smalls, listen to me.

26:30.050 --> 26:34.054
Go to that fence... real slow,
and be quiet.

26:34.179 --> 26:36.806
- But... I-I think--
- No, no, no. No, no.

26:36.890 --> 26:39.517
- Just go and peek through that hole.
- But I--

26:39.643 --> 26:43.521
- But I saw something. What's back there?
- It's okay. Just go.

26:43.647 --> 26:46.024
- Just go.
- Go, Smalls.

26:46.149 --> 26:48.026
Come on, Smalls.

26:49.861 --> 26:52.781
Shh!

27:03.333 --> 27:05.210
Shh!

27:10.090 --> 27:13.927
- Shh!
- Be quiet.

27:18.890 --> 27:20.809
