so how can I have some more of nothing?

27:56.594 --> 27:59.431
- Shut up!
- You're killing me, Smalls.

27:59.514 --> 28:02.767
- All right. Who cut one?
- These are s'mores stuff.

28:02.892 --> 28:05.854
- Okay, pay attention.
- Bertram!

28:05.937 --> 28:08.189
First you take the graham.

28:08.273 --> 28:11.985
You stick the chocolate
on the graham.

28:12.110 --> 28:15.155
- Then you roast the 'mallow.
- No, it's my sleeping bag.

28:15.280 --> 28:17.699
When the 'mallow's flaming,

28:17.782 --> 28:20.327
Yes, it is yours.
It has a yellow stain on it.

28:20.452 --> 28:22.662
You stick it
on the chocolate.

28:22.787 --> 28:25.123
- You're gonna set the place on fire.
- Then...

28:25.206 --> 28:28.126
