- Come on up, Wendy.

39:03.887 --> 39:07.265
Everybody move back.
Move back. Roll him over.

39:07.349 --> 39:09.643
Never mind! Never mind!

39:09.768 --> 39:13.229
Come on, Squints.

39:13.313 --> 39:15.065
- Come on, Squints.
- Come on!

39:15.148 --> 39:17.567
Squints!

39:17.651 --> 39:20.987
