to put the move on the lifeguard.

41:22.525 --> 41:25.195
He did.
He had kissed a woman,

41:25.320 --> 41:27.656
and he had kissed her long
and good.

41:27.739 --> 41:30.408
We got banned from the pool
forever that day.

41:30.533 --> 41:32.410
But every time we walked by
after that,

41:32.535 --> 41:34.412
the lifeguard looked down
from her tower,

41:34.537 --> 41:36.831
right over at Squints...

41:36.915 --> 41:40.085
and smiled.

41:52.055 --> 41:53.932
- Get your glove and come on.
- What's the big deal?

41:54.057 --> 41:57.769
- Night game. Come on. Come on.
- Mom, I'm going out!

42:14.327 --> 42:16.413
There was only one night game a year.

42:16.496 --> 42:18.665
- Guys, wait up!
- On the 4th of July...

42:18.790 --> 42:21.626
