44:13.905 --> 44:18.201
- Come on! Hurry up!
- First!

44:18.284 --> 44:20.537
Run!

44:20.620 --> 44:22.956
Back off!

44:24.457 --> 44:26.543
Yeah, yeah!

44:26.626 --> 44:30.005
- Throw it in! Throw it in!
- Get him! Get him!

44:30.088 --> 44:32.507
Come on! Come on!
Come on!

44:34.134 --> 44:36.761
- Come on! Hurry up!
- Go, Benny!

44:36.886 --> 44:40.223
Oh, damn!

44:45.312 --> 44:47.772
Oh, no!

45:16.468 --> 45:20.347
It's easy when you play with a bunch
of rejects and a fat kid, Rodriguez.

