be allowed to touch a baseball.

45:25.810 --> 45:28.688
Except for Rodriguez,
you're all an insult to the game.

45:28.813 --> 45:32.192
Come on! We'll take you on
right here, right now!

45:32.317 --> 45:35.695
Come on!

45:35.820 --> 45:38.073
We play on a real diamond, Porter.

45:38.156 --> 45:40.408
You ain't good enough to lick
the dirt off our cleats.

45:40.492 --> 45:42.911
- Watch it, jerk.
- Shut up, idiot!

45:42.994 --> 45:44.829
- Moron!
- Scab eater!

45:44.954 --> 45:46.956
- Butt sniffer!
- Pus licker!

45:47.040 --> 45:49.959
